Text.val: ... set addtional where clauses to select SCF_PARTICIPATION_CLIENT

ExpSyntax.val: 'exists(select * from '&Trim({32768,9})&'/ACCC where ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = SCPC_ADMNO and ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = SCPC_CLNTNO and ACCC_ACCT_DATE = '&''''&DStr({0,2},'YYYY-MM-DD')&''''&' and ACCC_MUTASETTLEMENT <> 0 and ACCC_MUTTYPE = 31)'
'not(exists(select * from '&Trim({32768,9})&'/RSDF where RSDF_ADMNO = SCPC_ADMNO and RSDF_CLNTNO = SCPC_CLNTNO and RSDF_DATE = '&''''&DStr({0,2},'YYYY-MM-DD')&''''&'))'

Text.val: -- Submit BXA418 outside current transaction to prevent trouble with JOBL row (if at least one SCPC row is selected)

SQL_STMT_U.val: select cast(sum(ACCC_MUTASETTLEMENT) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/ACCC where ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :2 and ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :3 and ACCC_ACCT_DATE = ':4' and ACCC_MUTTYPE = 31 for fetch only
